script.name: plugin.expguild.run
script.sourceplaintext:
* dont include in tutorial starts $start.group = get game start group id do if $start.group == 100 return null
$DEFINE.VERSION = 9 $DEFINE.LOGGING = [FALSE]
$version = get global variable: name='expguild.run'
* check for new version, incase patch needs to change the data if $DEFINE.VERSION > $version $pid = get global variable: name='expguild.pid' kill global script: pid=$pid $old.version = $version $version = null end
* create the discoveries * discoveries, [ * time, [ * race, [ * item, { * amounts * } * ] * ] * ]
* Predefined Discoveries * - Engine Tunings (15) * - Rudder Tunings (10) * - #deca.feda * - #deca.deaf * - #deca.cefa
$exp.data = get global variable: name='expguild.data' if not $exp.data $exp.data = table alloc
$discovery.data = table alloc $exp.data['discovery'] = $discovery.data $sector = get sector from universe index: x=3, y=5 do if $sector -> exists $exp.data['special.sector'] = $sector
* discoveryies at the beginning $race.table = table alloc $discovery.data[1] = $race.table
$data = table alloc $race.table[Pirates] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array
$data = table alloc $race.table[Player] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, null, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, null, null, null, null $data[#deca.fade ] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=4, 4, null, null, null $data[Scout] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=2, null, null, null, null if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $data[Enhanced Mercury] = $array else $data[Vulture Prototype] = $array end $array = create new array, arguments=5, null, null, null, null $data[Harrier Sentinel] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=50000, 25000, null, null, null $data[Credits] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, 1, 1 $data[Discovery] = $array
* discoveryies after 12 hours $race.table = table alloc $discovery.data[43200] = $race.table $data = table alloc $race.table[Xenon] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $data = table alloc $race.table[Player] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, null, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, null, null, null, null $data[#deca.deaf ] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=4, 4, null, null, null $data[Interceptor] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=2, null, null, null, null if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $data[Advanced Express] = $array else $data[Toucan Prototype] = $array end $array = create new array, arguments=2, null, null, null, null if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $data[Starburst] = $array else $data[Arrow] = $array end $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, 1, 1 $data[Discovery] = $array
* discoveryies after 24 hours $race.table = table alloc $discovery.data[86400] = $race.table $data = table alloc $race.table[Pirates] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, null, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $data = table alloc $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, 1, 1 $data[Special Discovery] = $array $race.table[Xenon] = $data $data = table alloc $race.table[Player] = $data $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, null, null, null $data[Pandora Tunings] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, null, null, null, null $data[#deca.cefa ] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=4, null, null, null, null $data[Fighter] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=2, null, null, null, null $data[LX ] = $array $array = create new array, arguments=1, 1, 1, 1, 1 $data[Discovery] = $array
$current.time = playing time $exp.data['last.goody'] = $current.time
@ = wait 2000 ms end
* add viable sectors $kingdom.end = get sector from universe index: x=0, y=0 $data = table alloc $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y if $sector -> exists if is valid route between sectors $sector and $kingdom.end $data[$sector] = $sector end end end end $exp.data['sectors'] = $data
@ = wait 2000 ms
$hq = get player HQ
* find rare blueprints $table.common = table alloc $table.rare = table alloc $table.station = table alloc $aRaces = get race array: include fixed=[FALSE], include corporations=[TRUE], include player=[FALSE] $i = size of array $aRaces while $i dec $i = $race = $aRaces[$i] do if $race == Unknown OR $race == Xenon OR $race == Kha'ak continue $plot.flags = get plot flags if ! ( $plot.flags & 1024 ) do if $race == Terran OR $race == ATF continue end
$avaialble.ships = table alloc
$shipyards = get station array: of race $race class/type=Shipyard $shipyard.i = size of array $shipyards while $shipyard.i dec $shipyard.i = $shipyard = $shipyards[$shipyard.i] $products = $shipyard -> get tradeable ware array from station $product.i = size of array $products while $product.i dec $product.i = $product = $products[$product.i] $maintype = get maintype of ware $product if $maintype == [SSTYPE_SHIP] $avaialble.ships[$product] = $product else if $maintype == [SSTYPE_FACTORY] if $hq -> exists skip if $hq ->player HQ has blueprints for: type=$product $table.station[$product] = $product else $table.station[$product] = $product end end end end
@ = wait 10 ms
@ $diplomacy.ships = [THIS] -> call script !agent.cmd.specialships.menu : Diplomat=null State='data' Last Value=$race do if $diplomacy.ships $diplomacy.ships = convert array to table: $diplomacy.ships, increment=[FALSE]
$aShips = get all ship types: class=Moveable Ship race=$race $ships.i = size of array $aShips while $ships.i dec $ships.i = $shiptype = $aShips[$ships.i] $maker.race = get maker race: shiptype=$shiptype skip if $maker.race == $race continue
if $hq -> exists do if $hq ->player HQ has blueprints for: type=$shiptype continue end
if $diplomacy.ships do if $diplomacy.ships[$shiptype] continue end
if $avaialble.ships[$shiptype] $table.common[$shiptype] = $shiptype else $table.rare[$shiptype] = $shiptype end end @ = wait 100 ms end
$table.planet.radius = table alloc $table.planet.radius[48] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[49] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[50] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[51] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[52] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[53] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[54] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[55] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[56] = 591000
$table.planet.radius[57] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[58] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[59] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[60] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[61] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[62] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[63] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[64] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[65] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[66] = 650000 $table.planet.radius[67] = 650000
$exp.data['planet.radius'] = $table.planet.radius $exp.data['common.ships'] = $table.common $exp.data['rare.ships'] = $table.rare $exp.data['stations'] = $table.station set global variable: name='expguild.data' value=$exp.data
* Check any spawned locations if they are in planets and move them if $old.version <= 2 AND ! $version $created.discoveries = $exp.data['created.discoveries'] if $created.discoveries $obj = get next key: table=$created.discoveries key=null while $obj if $obj -> exists $pos.array = $obj -> get position as array $sector = $obj -> get sector gosub sub.CheckInPlanet if $ret.InPlanet $attempts = 10 gosub sub.GetLocationPosition if not $ret.PosFailed $obj ->set position: x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z else $race = $sector -> get owner race gosub sub.GetLocation $obj ->put into environment $sector $obj ->set position: x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z end end end $obj = get next key: table=$created.discoveries key=$obj end end @ = wait 100 ms end
do if $version return null
set global variable: name='expguild.run' value=$DEFINE.VERSION $pid = get PID set global variable: name='expguild.pid' value=$pid
$created.discoveries = $exp.data['created.discoveries'] if not $created.discoveries $created.discoveries = table alloc $exp.data['created.discoveries'] = $created.discoveries end
$created.special.discoveries = $exp.data['created.special.discoveries'] if not $created.special.discoveries $created.special.discoveries = table alloc $exp.data['created.special.discoveries'] = $created.special.discoveries end
$created.random.discovery = $exp.data['created.random.discoveries'] if not $created.random.discovery $created.random.discovery = table alloc $exp.data['created.random.discoveries'] = $created.random.discovery end
$created.xenon.discoveries = $exp.data['created.xenon.discoveries'] if not $created.xenon.discoveries $created.xenon.discoveries = table alloc $exp.data['created.xenon.discoveries'] = $created.xenon.discoveries end
$sector.points = $exp.data['sector.points'] if not $sector.points $sector.points = table alloc $exp.data['sector.points'] = $sector.points end
$discovery.large.range = [FALSE]
while get global variable: name='expguild.run' @ = wait randomly from 30000 to 60000 ms
* remove any gates in hsap sectors that are deactived if not $exp.data['rem.hsap'] $playing.time = playing time if $playing.time > 120 $exp.data['rem.hsap'] = [TRUE] $x = get max sectors in x direction while $x dec $x = $y = get max sectors in y direction while $y dec $y = $sector = get sector from universe index: x=$x, y=$y skip if $sector -> exists continue $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race skip if $sector.owner continue skip if $sector ->is sector proposed continue $flags = [Find.Hyperspeed] | [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] $hsap = find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null skip if $hsap -> exists continue $hsap ->set owner race to Neutral Race $hsap = $hsap -> get gate destination: return sector=[FALSE] $hsap ->set owner race to Neutral Race do if $hsap ->is hsap discoverable continue skip if $hsap ->is hyperspeed locked continue
$gates = find gate: flags=[Find.Multiple], refobj=$sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if $gates $i = size of array $gates while $i dec $i = $gate = $gates[$i] $gate ->destruct: show no explosion=[TRUE] end end end @ = wait 1 ms end end end
$created.discoveries = $exp.data['created.discoveries'] $created.random.discovery = $exp.data['created.random.discoveries'] $created.special.discoveries = $exp.data['created.special.discoveries'] $created.xenon.discoveries = $exp.data['created.xenon.discoveries'] $sector.points = $exp.data['sector.points'] $sector.data = $exp.data['sectors']
if $created.discoveries $next.obj = get next key: table=$created.discoveries key=null while $next.obj $obj = $next.obj $next.obj = get next key: table=$created.discoveries key=$next.obj
if $obj -> exists $obj.sector = $obj -> get sector do if $obj -> exists continue end remove key $obj from table $created.discoveries do if $created.random.discovery remove key $obj from table $created.random.discovery do if $created.special.discoveries remove key $obj from table $created.special.discoveries do if $created.xenon.discoveries remove key $obj from table $created.xenon.discoveries end end
@ = wait 100 ms
* check if the ai should claim a sector if $exp.data['player.hsap'] if $exp.data['player.built.toa'] $expire.time = $exp.data['npc.hsap.expire'] $playing.time = playing time if ( ! $expire.time OR $expire.time < $playing.time ) AND $expire.time != -1 @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.expguild.npcclaim : end else $hsap.sector = $exp.data['last.hsap.sector'] if $hsap.sector -> exists $flags = [Find.ExcludeGates] | [Find.ExcludeTerranGates] | [Find.Hyperspeed] if not find gate: flags=$flags, refobj=$hsap.sector, max dist=null, refpos=null if find gate: flags=[Find.ExcludeGates], refobj=$hsap.sector, max dist=null, refpos=null $exp.data['player.built.toa'] = [TRUE] end end end end end
* do the timed discoveries $current.time = playing time $discovery.data = $exp.data['discovery'] if $discovery.data $time = get next key: table=$discovery.data key=null while $time $next = get next key: table=$discovery.data key=$time if $current.time > $time $race.table = $discovery.data[$time]
$race = get random key: table=$race.table $data = $race.table[$race] $item = get random key: table=$data $array = $data[$item] if $array if size of array $array $array.size = size of array $array $rnd = random value from 0 to $array.size - 1 $count = $array[$rnd] remove element from array $array at index $rnd $enhanced.points = [TRUE] gosub sub.DoGoody end
skip if size of array $array remove key $item from table $data else remove key $item from table $data end skip if size of table $data remove key $race from table $race.table skip if size of table $race.table remove key $time from table $discovery.data end $time = $next end
skip if size of table $discovery.data remove key 'discovery' from table $exp.data end
@ = wait 1000 ms
* create random discoveries $discovery.large.range = [TRUE] $enhanced.points = [TRUE]
$current.time = playing time if $current.time > 100000 $race = Xenon $last.time = $exp.data['last.goody.xenon'] skip if $last.time $last.time = 0 if $current.time > ( $last.time + 3600 ) $exp.data['last.goody.xenon'] = $current.time
$next.obj = get next key: table=$created.xenon.discoveries key=null while $next.obj $obj = $next.obj $next.obj = get next key: table=$created.xenon.discoveries key=$next.obj skip if $obj -> exists remove key $obj from table $created.xenon.discoveries end $size = size of table $created.xenon.discoveries if $size < 3 gosub sub.GetSpecial $count = 1 gosub sub.DoGoody if $obj -> exists $created.xenon.discoveries[$obj] = [TRUE] end end end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
$race = Player $last.time = $exp.data['last.good.special'] skip if $last.time $last.time = 0 $current.time = playing time if $current.time > ( $last.time + 7200 ) $exp.data['last.goody.special'] = $current.time
$next.obj = get next key: table=$created.special.discoveries key=null while $next.obj $obj = $next.obj $next.obj = get next key: table=$created.special.discoveries key=$next.obj skip if $obj -> exists remove key $obj from table $created.special.discoveries end $size = size of table $created.special.discoveries if $size < 5 gosub sub.GetSpecial $count = 1 gosub sub.DoGoody if $obj -> exists $created.special.discoveries[$obj] = [TRUE] end end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
$race = Player $discovery.large.range = [FALSE] $enhanced.points = [FALSE] $last.time = $exp.data['last.goody'] skip if $last.time $last.time = 0 $current.time = playing time if $current.time > ( $last.time + 1800 ) $exp.data['last.goody'] = $current.time
$next.obj = get next key: table=$created.random.discovery key=null while $next.obj $obj = $next.obj $next.obj = get next key: table=$created.random.discovery key=$next.obj skip if $obj -> exists remove key $obj from table $created.random.discovery end
$size = size of table $created.random.discovery if $size < 5 if not random value from 0 to 10 - 1 $item = Special Discovery $count = 1 else $rnd = random value from 0 to 4 - 1 if $rnd == 0 $item = Credits $count = random value from 100 to 1000 - 1 else if $rnd == 1 $rnd = random value from 0 to 5 - 1 if $rnd == 0 $item = Silicon Wafers else if $rnd == 1 $item = Crystals else if $rnd == 2 $item = Microchips else if $rnd == 3 $item = Computer Components else $item = Energy Cells end $count = random value from 10 to 20 - 1 else $item = Discovery $count = 1 end end gosub sub.DoGoody if $obj -> exists $created.random.discovery[$obj] = [TRUE] end end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
* assign sector points $last.time = $exp.data['last.sector'] $current.time = playing time if $current.time > ( $last.time + 1200 ) $exp.data['last.sector'] = $current.time
$next = get next key: table=$sector.points key=null while $next $sector = $next $next = get next key: table=$sector.points key=$next skip if $sector ->get discovery points remove key $sector from table $sector.points end
$size = size of table $sector.points if $size < 5 while [TRUE] $sector = get random key: table=$sector.data if not $sector.points[$sector] if not $sector ->get discovery points $points = 5000 $sector ->set discovery points: points=$points $sector.points[$sector] = $points break end end end end end
end
return null
sub.GetSpecial: if not random value from 0 to 20 - 1 $item = Pandora Tunings else if not random value from 0 to 20 - 1 $races = create new array, size=11, elements=Argon, Boron, Split, Paranid, Teladi, Terran, Xenon, Pirates $races[8] = Yaki $races[9] = OTAS $races[10] = Atreus $race = get random array item: array=$races $rnd = random value from 0 to 100 - 1 $item = null if $rnd >= 90 $item = get random ship type: class=M3 race=$race else if $rnd >= 60 $item = get random ship type: class=M4 race=$race else if $rnd >= 50 $item = get random ship type: class=TP race=$race else if $rnd >= 40 $item = get random ship type: class=TS race=$race else $item = get random ship type: class=M5 race=$race end skip if $item $item = get random ship type: class=Fighter race=$race skip if $item $item = Boarding Pod else if not random value from 0 to 20 - 1 $arr = array alloc: size=6 $arr[0] = Incendiary Bomb Launcher $arr[1] = Phased Array Laser Cannon $arr[2] = Fusion Beam Cannon $arr[3] = Tri-Beam Cannon $arr[4] = Plasma Beam Cannon $arr[5] = Boarding Pod $item = get random array item: array=$arr else $item = Special Discovery end endsub
sub.DoGoody: if $enhanced.points $points = 10000 else $points = 5000 end if $item @ $obj = [THIS] -> call script plugin.expguild.spawn : Race=$race Item=$item Quantity=$count Points=$points Large Radius=$discovery.large.range Blueprint?=[FALSE] if $obj $created.discoveries[$obj] = $obj end end endsub
sub.GetLocation: if $race == Player $sub.table = $sector.data else $sub.table = table alloc $sector = get next key: table=$sector.data key=null while $sector $sector.owner = $sector -> get owner race if $sector.owner == $race $sub.table[$sector] = $sector end $sector = get next key: table=$sector.data key=$sector end end
while size of table $sub.table $sector = get random key: table=$sub.table $attempts = 20 gosub sub.GetLocationPosition skip if $ret.PosFailed break remove key $sector from table $sector.data remove key $sector from table $sub.table @ = wait 10 ms end endsub
sub.GetLocationPosition: $ret.PosFailed = [FALSE] $try.again = [TRUE] while $attempts > 0 AND $try.again dec $attempts = $try.again = [FALSE] if $discovery.large.range $dist = $sector -> get size of object $dist = $dist * 2 $max.dist = $dist * 2
$pos.x = random value from $dist to $max.dist - 1 $pos.y = random value from 15000 to 35000 - 1 $pos.z = random value from $dist to $max.dist - 1 else $dist = $sector -> get size of object $max.dist = $dist * 2
$pos.x = random value from $dist to $max.dist - 1 $pos.y = random value from 5000 to 25000 - 1 $pos.z = random value from $dist to $max.dist - 1 end
do if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $pos.x = - $pos.x do if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $pos.y = - $pos.y do if random value from 0 to 2 - 1 $pos.z = - $pos.z
$pos.array = create new array, arguments=$pos.x, $pos.y, $pos.z, null, null gosub sub.CheckInPlanet if $ret.InPlanet @ = wait 10 ms $try.again = [TRUE] end end do if $attempts <= 0 AND $try.again $ret.PosFailed = [TRUE] endsub
sub.CreateCrate: $obj = create flying ware: maintype=$maintype subtype=$subtype count=$count sector=$sector x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z selfdestruct=[FALSE] $obj ->set flying ware secret: [TRUE] $obj ->set invincible: enabled=[TRUE] endsub
sub.CreateShip: $obj = create ship: type=$item owner=Neutral Race addto=$sector x=$pos.x y=$pos.y z=$pos.z if $count == 2 $obj ->install ship size wares: type=[ShipWare.S] else if $count == 3 $obj ->install ship size wares: type=[ShipWare.M] else if $count == 4 $obj ->install ship size wares: type=[ShipWare.L] if $item == Scout = $obj -> install 1 units of Alpha Kyon Emitter else if $item == Interceptor = $obj -> install 2 units of Alpha Kyon Emitter else if $item == Fighter = $obj -> install 3 units of Beta Kyon Emitter end else if $count == 5 $obj ->add default items to ship: loadout=[ShipLoad.Minimum], marines=[FALSE] else if $count == 6 $obj ->add default items to ship: loadout=[ShipLoad.Average], marines=[FALSE] else if $count == 7 $obj ->add default items to ship: loadout=[ShipLoad.Maximum], marines=[FALSE] end endsub
sub.DoDiscovery: if $obj -> exists $obj.sector = $obj -> get sector $dist = $obj.sector -> get size of object if $discovery.large.range $min.dist = 100000 else $min.dist = 150000 end $obj.pos = $obj -> get position as array $centre.pos = create new array, arguments=0, 0, 0, null, null $centre.dist = get distance: position array1=$obj.pos array2=$centre.pos $centre.dist = $centre.dist / 2 $dist = get maximum, $dist, $min.dist, $centre.dist, null, null $obj ->set LFL target: [TRUE], range=$dist if $enhanced.points $points = 10000 else $points = 5000 end $obj ->set discovery points: points=$points $created.discoveries[$obj] = $obj
if $DEFINE.LOGGING $obj.sector = $obj -> get sector $pos = $obj -> get position as array write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Normal], fmt='Discovery Created: %s, Sector=%s (%s) Points=%s', $obj, $obj.sector, $pos, $points, null end end endsub
sub.CheckInPlanet: $ret.InPlanet = [FALSE] $planets = $sector -> get planet array if $planets $i.p = size of array $planets while $i.p dec $i.p = $planet = $planets[$i.p] $planet.pos = $planet -> get position as array $planet.dist = get distance: position array1=$pos.array array2=$planet.pos gosub sub.GetPlanetRadius if $planet.dist < $planet.radius $ret.InPlanet = [TRUE] break end end end endsub
sub.GetPlanetRadius: $planet.radius = 100000 *$planet.radius = 650000 $table.planet.radius = $exp.data['planet.radius'] if $table.planet.radius $planet.sub = $planet -> get subtype $planet.radius = $table.planet.radius[$planet.sub] end endsub return null
